aExCopyContentPlugin

This plugin adds a button that copies the default culture content of the page to the current culture. The button is located under "This Page" button.

INSTALLATION
- Add aExCopyContentPlugin to the list of enabled plugins in config/ProjectConfiguration.class.php
- Add copyContent to the list of enabled modules in settings.yml
- Override the a/breadcrumbExtra partial (file app/frontend/modules/a/templates/_breadcrumbExra.php) and add the following line to it:
<?php include_partial("copyContent/button", array('page' => $page)); ?>

USAGE
